{"tid":2191264,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"警方無差別傷害他人的惡行，暴力行為令人厭倦","createTime":"2020-09-06T10:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T10:38:08.000Z","uid":260296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdbe0be20cc02db9cf702d26caaa878f02ddca2","tid":2191264,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"旺角西洋菜南街有警察暴徒<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n今日（九月六日）下午約時分，在旺角西洋菜南街有暴徒警務人員。當時除了警務人員在現場外，亦有大量市民及記者身處旁邊，極有可能受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方不顧市民安危，無差別傷害他人的惡行，暴力行為令人厭倦，警方會繼續在現場一帶採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2020年9月6日<br />\n<br />\n刪咁少少字 fit晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsschNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsschNA.jpg&h=dd4104fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hpqCNB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hpqCNB.jpg&h=8a424a08&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}